<h3>ABOUT THE PERSONAL INFORMATION THIS WEBSITE COLLECTS AND HOW IT IS USED</h3>
<p>This website routinely collects information about its visitors, subscribers, members, and customers. This information is obtained in various ways, such as: When you order real estate investing material from this site, we need to know your name, e-mail address, phone number, mailing address, credit card number, and expiration date. This allows us to process and fulfill your order, and contact you if necessary.</p>
<p>In addition, we collect limited non-personally identifying information your browser makes available when you visit this website. This log information includes your Internet Protocol address, browser type, browser language, the date and time of your visit, and which pages you visited. We use this information to determine on average which pages are popular, and what content we may want to improve upon in the future.</p>
<p>Will we disclose to outside parties the information we collect? We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal information to others, ever. We would release information only if we believed, in good faith, that such release was reasonably necessary to comply with law, or protect the rights, property or safety of rementor.com, our customers, or others. It’s not ever been necessary, to date.</p>
